0.01 - Current Unreleased Version


0.1
 * stop a container
 * start a container
 * destroy a container via lxc-destroy
 * create a container via lxc-create
 * freeze a container
 * unfreeze a container
 * proper command line parsing
 * working status as there was in rlxc

0.2
 * all strings are translated
 * generating of ssh keys
 * updateing of ssh keys in clients
 * setting up of ssh service in guests
 * entering guests via ssh
 * executing commands via ssh

0.3
 * native destroying of containers
 * diagnostics of lxc system
 * netstat for containers

0.4
 * native container creation, even if crude
